{"tid":1258545,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]香港三家銀行決定取消最低結餘服務費！","createTime":"2019-06-26T07:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:28:30.000Z","uid":157012,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b550bdbf4111421651f547816f44a872766be1a","tid":1258545,"uid":157012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"撰文：Market Digest Editorial 2019-06-26 15:00<br />\n渣打(2888)宣布，由8月1日起，取消個人綜合理財服務「Premium理財」及「快易理財」的最低結餘服務費。<br />\n<br />\n同時，非綜合理財個人客戶存款戶口之小額存款收費及Click-a-Count存款客戶之櫃台交易服務費亦會取消，以滿足不同市民對銀行服務的需要。<br />\n<br />\n渣打表示，一直支持本港普及金融及智慧銀行的發展，以其為首的財團是首批成功取得營運虛擬銀行牌照的銀行，是次取消個人客戶最低結餘服務費，進一步體現渣打為普羅大眾提供基本銀行服務的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n早前，匯豐（0005）及中銀香港（2388）亦分別宣布自8月1日起，全面取消個人綜合理財及一般賬戶的服務費。<br />\n<br />\n同時間，有報道指恒生銀行亦正籌備豁免最低結餘收費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://marketdigest.io/article/108/bankcancelfee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmarketdigest.io%2Farticle%2F108%2Fbankcancelfee&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=d780ed1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://marketdigest.io/article/108/bankcancelfee</a>"},{"pid":"520191db7c95a860be4e496ddc8b7b9f6bccdf50","tid":1258545,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"幾時到citi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a18ace407da4b2c91c882bd99d5dfe35af797ab","tid":1258545,"uid":33872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"搶客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nboc今次真係俾人分"},{"pid":"a6833ea000e08627e0d8a3f4e263f39f581c3b5f","tid":1258545,"uid":157012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6a18ace407da4b2c91c882bd99d5dfe35af797ab","tid":1258545,"uid":33872,"like":0